<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef865e4a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2544"><num value="2544">§ 2544.</num><heading> Research exemption</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The use and reproduction of a protected variety for plant breeding or other bona fide research shall not constitute an infringement of the protection provided under this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef865e4b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/577/tIII/s114">Pub. L. 91–577, title III, § 114</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1555">84 Stat. 1555</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
